Package common.structure

Class Stack<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • common.structure.Stack<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Type of objects stored in a stack.
    public class Stack<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Implementation of simple stack (LIFO). Stack can hold unlimited amount of items or (if limit is not zero), fixed amount of items. If stack limit is present and amount of stored items is already equals to limit, then the bottomest item is removed from the stack.

    • Field Summary

      int limit
